-- Portugal Telecom Needs to Sell Vivo Stake in July, El Economista Reports
-- Paul Tobin
-- 2010-07-20T05:28:48Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-20/portugal-telecom-needs-to-sell-vivo-stake-in-july-el-economista-reports.html

          
          
             Portugal Telecom SGPS SA  needs to
complete the sale of its stake in  Vivo Participacoes SA  this
month, before a contract to invest in  Tele Norte Leste
Participacoes SA  expires,  El Economista  reported, citing
unidentified people in the financial industry.  
 Telefonica SA will maintain its 7.15 billion-euro offer for
the stake, the paper said.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
